    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, showcasing a flawless 3.6L flat-six powerplant equipped with VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing. This widebody example features the highly sought-after 6-speed Getrag manual transaxle, delivering power through a sophisticated viscous-coupling AWD system. The chassis is anchored by Turbo-spec four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors, ensuring exceptional thermal management. Meticulously maintained with zero evidence of bore scoring and a documented IMS bearing retrofit. The factory Arctic Silver finish maintains consistent paint depth across all panels, and the suspension geometry remains true to original factory tolerances. A mechanically superlative specimen for the discerning collector.",
