      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, maintained in showroom condition since the day it was driven off the lot. The exterior boasts a flawless factory finish with a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirls, stone chips, or door dings. Every panel gap is perfectly aligned, and the alloy wheels are completely free of curb rash, wrapped in premium tires with near-full tread. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather upholstery still retains its factory scent and shows absolutely no signs of wear, bolsters are firm, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. All technological features, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced navigation, function exactly as they did when new. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule. This car comes with a complete service history from authorized dealerships, two original key fobs, and the original owner\u2019s manual. It has been garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. For a buyer seeking perfection, this is the definitive choice.",
